Node inspector
Using web sockets so you can open and debug using developer tools from your browser.


Install with npm


- Inspecting elements
- Watching elements
- Next function call
- Live edit
- debugger to programatically insert breakpoints

Remote debugging
- http://10.192.61.67:8080/debug?port=5858

Embed into other applications


It's a bit flaky, but definitely a very useful tools

